WELCOME TO CROP
===============

1 Getting Start

If you see me, it means you have unpacked crop_x.y.z.tar.gz.
Now, the only thing you need to do is Enter:

   [root@localhost crop_x.y.z]# pwd
   /tmp/crop_x.y.z
   [root@localhost crop_x.y.z]# ./install.sh
   current directory </tmp/crop_x.y.z> will be the DFCHOME.
   /tmp/crop_x.y.z is the work space.

or

   [root@localhost crop_x.y.z]# ./install.sh /tmp/test
   </tmp/test> is a valid directory, now <crop_x.y.z> will be installed there.
   /tmp/test/crop_x.y.z is the work space.

Reentry your user account, or enter "source ~/.bash_profile" to make the self-starting in operation.
Remember: here it is  "$DFCHOME/bin/your_program_name".

2 Self-starting
The flowing command can make your program self-starting.
   sudo sh -c "echo 'su - dm -c \"your_program_name\"' sudo >>/etc/rc.d/rc.local"
Enjoy~





欢迎使用Crop
===============

1 开始使用

你解压了我，不能一笑而过。现在还得输入下面几条命令：

   [root@localhost crop_x.y.z]# pwd
   /tmp/crop_x.y.z
   [root@localhost crop_x.y.z]# ./install.sh
   current directory </tmp/crop_x.y.z> will be the DFCHOME.
   /tmp/crop_x.y.z is the work space.

或者

   [root@localhost crop_x.y.z]# ./install.sh /tmp/test
   </tmp/test> is a valid directory, now <crop_x.y.z> will be installed there.
   /tmp/test/crop_x.y.z is the work space.

重新进入一下你所在的账户或 source ~/.bash_profile 使环境变量生效。
哦了，现在你可以玩你的程序了~ 记住，它在这里：$DFCHOME/bin/你的程序名

2 开机自启动
使用下面的命令，让你的程序随叫随到：
   
   sudo sh -c "echo 'su - dm -c \"你的程序名\"' sudo >>/etc/rc.d/rc.local"

你可能会遇到 “xxx is not in the sudoers file.  This incident will be reported.”的问题，
root下编辑/etc/sudoers，在root ALL=(ALL)ALL行下添加xxx ALL=(ALL)ALL，xxx为你的用户名。

